{"tid":1734350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去新加坡要Visa？","createTime":"2019-11-18T10:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T10:41:04.000Z","uid":13268,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"06f7f7e219ef619f48dfcbfd06fd95368b6d4939","tid":1734350,"uid":13268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:06:08.000Z","msg":"因為工作需要，間中都會幫人申請新加坡visa。頭先見到另一個Post入面好多人話香港人去新加坡要visa，睇返原post條link係講緊&rdquo;for holder of Hong Kong Document of Identity&rdquo;, 唔係&rdquo;Hong Kong SAR passport / BNO&rdquo;呀<br />\n<br />\n未見過Hong Kong Document of Identity既請睇下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpJgVPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpJgVPB.jpg&h=ba7b88d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揸呢本野去新加坡不嬲都要Visa架，但HKSAR/BNO護照就唔使。各位唔好亂信fake news喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持新加坡警察嚴正執法！後果自負！後果自負！"},{"pid":"629711a1fd9f7266e17ae2d738e6d94a58c67565","tid":1734350,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"其實咩人先攞到呢本嘢？新移民？"},{"pid":"b820cd30817569218ba9bc935efb8e00411eeb33","tid":1734350,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"629711a1fd9f7266e17ae2d738e6d94a58c67565","tid":1734350,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"其實咩人先攞到呢本嘢？新移民？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:09:55.000Z","msg":"未住夠七年"},{"pid":"b26d22e9c3436a38df68455e1b2544549e56e385","tid":1734350,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"629711a1fd9f7266e17ae2d738e6d94a58c67565","tid":1734350,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"其實咩人先攞到呢本嘢？新移民？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:10:10.000Z","msg":"未住夠七年"},{"pid":"b8ea21c2dab00a13419aeeb0511182da1824af3b","tid":1734350,"uid":13268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"629711a1fd9f7266e17ae2d738e6d94a58c67565","tid":1734350,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"其實咩人先攞到呢本嘢？新移民？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"以我所知係為上面落黎香港，因為係香港未住夠7年未係永久居民，所以申請唔到特區護照既人而設。佢地需要去外地就要申請呢本野當護照咁用。因為上面冇寫係passport，又唔係多人用同唔常見，好多外國immigration見到都左check右check，好麻煩既一本三不象。"},{"pid":"0e47b56e1503d56a4bf408264cb2cd010b5f62ae","tid":1734350,"uid":5125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"呢本野仲衰過bno"},{"pid":"8b3d7f421f033e3c47b9c6d858adb98e4177e89a","tid":1734350,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e47b56e1503d56a4bf408264cb2cd010b5f62ae","tid":1734350,"uid":5125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"呢本野仲衰過bno"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:19:26.000Z","msg":"連支那護照都衰過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDI一路都係地底泥"},{"pid":"7b2ab073c1d823ef4c0ffa780970b920a90910da","tid":1734350,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"英治時期已經有CI 同DI，係去邊都要簽證"}]}